hcc_text: Rockaway Freeway is in the middle third in Queens for pedestrian deaths and serious injuries per mile.
info: At Rockaway Freeway at Far Rockaway Boulevard, Bay 25th Street and Beach 25th Street, there were 9 injuries in crashes between 2008 and 2012.
